---
title: Sundried Tomato, Mushroom & Parmesan Fettucine with Golden Pine Nuts
description: You won’t believe how delicious the end result of this pasta is. Cream and stock infuse the fettuccine with beautiful sauciness and flavour, leaving you with perfect strands of pasta is covered in silky mushrooms and sundried tomatoes.
